--1.Raskite produktą, kuris yra parduodamas --daugiausiai kartų kaip kitas produktas papildomose užsakymų eilutėse (order_details) -- --select p.product_id, p.product_name, count(od.order_id) as additional_order_count --from products p --join order_details od ON p.product_id = od.product_id ----filtruojam produktus kurie yra parduodami daugiau kartu nei kiti produktai --where --(select count(od1.order_id) from order_details od1 --where p.product_id = od1.product_id) > ----skaiciuojam visus kitus uzsakymus kuriuose yra sis produktas------------- --(select count(od3.order_id) from order_details od3 --where p.product_id = od3.product_id and od3.order_id <> od.order_id) ----skaiciuoja visu kitu uzsakymu kieki kuriuose buvo sis produktas------------- --group by p.product_id, p.product_name --order by additional_order_count desc limit 2;

--select customer_id, count(*) as order_count, sum(order_total) as total_amount from ( --select o.customer_id, o.order_id, sum(od.quantity * od.unit_price) as order_total from orders o --join order_details od on o.order_id = od.order_id --group by o.customer_id, o.order_id) as subquery --groub by customer_id --having count(*) >1 and sum(order_total) <1000
